overview: The love story revolves around the melodious music that begins when the young Na Na Na named "Kao Klao" (New-Chaiyaphon Julian Phu Part) starts to collide with "Thongkon" (Pang-Prakit Bo Suwan) that the father-in-law is willing to give up "Thongkwao" (Praew - Chaimawi Suwan Phanuchok), a beautiful daughter to give But there is only one condition that "I have to pay ten thousand thousand dowry!" Where will he earn money from ten thousand? Where? And it's time for the premiere of "Chicken Fight!"
title: Mon Love 10 Muen
